    <div class="row oldschool">
        <div class="col-md-12">
            You want a few guidelines to learn how to learn vocabulary the old school way? Follow these instructions!
            <p>
                If you are not afraid of trashing your books, write annotations on the edge of pages!
                It's not easy to read, not easy to learn, and it's very boring!
            </p>
            <div class="picture">
                <img src="/bundles/ovskiwebsite/img/scbook.jpg">
            </div>
