            </p>
            <p>
                Well, yes it's a little extreme, but just think about what this app can do for you:
            <ul>
                <li>Usable anywhere as long as you have an internet connection <i class="fa fa-check"></i></li>
                <li>Never get crumpled or torn <i class="fa fa-check"></i></li>
                <li>You actively participate in the fight against deforestation <i class="fa fa-check"></i></li>
                <li>You will finally have a good excuse to use your smartphone in language courses <i class="fa fa-check"></i></li>
            </ul>
